# 🐧 LinuxSujith – The Ultimate Curated Tool Repository

Welcome to **LinuxSujith**, your one-stop GitHub repository for discovering and exploring 800+ hand-picked tools across AI, productivity, content creation, coding, automation, education, and more.

This repository serves as a **digital toolbox** and **knowledge map** for students, developers, creators, entrepreneurs, and tech enthusiasts.

---

## 🚀 What’s Inside?

Explore categorized tools for:

| Category | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| 🖼️ Image & Video | Edit, enhance, and create using AI and online tools |
| 🎵 Music & Voice | AI-generated music, text-to-speech, and audio cleanup |
| 📄 Writing & Content | Paraphrasers, grammar tools, AI blog generators |
| 🧠 AI Tools | Chatbots, AI search engines, coding assistants |
| 📊 Productivity | Task managers, planners, calendars, and note-takers |
| 🗂️ Project Management | Kanban boards, dashboards, collaboration apps |
| 📚 Learning | Courses, tutorials, and online schools |
| 🧩 No-Code/Low-Code | App builders, form creators, internal tools |
| 🔐 Privacy & Security | Background removers, secure file sharing, VPNs |
| 💬 Marketing & Social | Email marketing, link-in-bio tools, schedulers |
| 🌐 Website Builders | Drag-and-drop site creators, CMS tools |
| 💼 Freelancing & Remote Work | Job boards, portfolios, and client tools |

