# 🤖 AI Tools Directory – Curated by LinuxSujith

Welcome to the **AI Tools Directory**, a comprehensive collection of **850+ AI-powered tools and websites** designed for creators, developers, students, freelancers, marketers, and productivity lovers.

This GitHub repo is maintained by **LinuxSujith**, showcasing tools for:
- Image & design editing
- Productivity boosters
- Content generation
- Learning & note-taking
- Audio/video enhancement
- No-code app building
...and much more!

---

## 📂 About This Project

This repository contains a categorized list of AI tools across different industries. Each tool includes:
- Name
- Use case
- Direct website link

Whether you’re creating a design, building a project, writing content, or automating workflows—this directory helps you discover the right AI for the job.

